OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be cloudy with some outbreaks of
OL,7,Frain, occasionally on the heavy side.
OL,8,FThen the rest of the night will be
OL,9,Fcloudy but rain turning light and
OL,10,Fpatchy. Winds easing.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FRather cloudy with occasional
OL,13,Fmainly light rain. Becoming mainly dry
OL,14,Flater with perhaps some brightness
OL,15,Ftowards Deeside and the south.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FA
OL,18,Fmainly dry few days with variable
OL,19,Famounts of cloud and some spells of
OL,20,Fsunshine. Perhaps some heavy showers
OL,21,Flate Friday. Very warm or hot.
